import React from "react"
import ContentLoader from "react-content-loader"

const BookmarkLoader = (props) => (
  <ContentLoader 
    speed={2}
    width={800}
    height={1050}
    viewBox="0 0 800 1050"
    backgroundColor="#f3f3f3"
    foregroundColor="#ecebeb"
    {...props}
  >
    <rect x="31" y="130" rx="0" ry="0" width="0" height="9" /> 
    <rect x="8" y="17" rx="0" ry="0" width="150" height="14" /> 
    <rect x="8" y="50" rx="0" ry="0" width="1200" height="5" /> 
    <circle cx="31" cy="105" r="28" /> 
    <rect x="80" y="93" rx="0" ry="0" width="123" height="10" /> 
    <rect x="80" y="111" rx="0" ry="0" width="150" height="10" /> 
    <rect x="1120" y="83" rx="0" ry="0" width="50" height="10" /> 
    <rect x="1180" y="79" rx="0" ry="0" width="19" height="16" /> 
    <rect x="8" y="148" rx="0" ry="0" width="1200" height="10" /> 
    <rect x="8" y="179" rx="5" ry="5" width="1200" height="233" /> 
    <circle cx="27" cy="452" r="19" /> 
    <circle cx="77" cy="452" r="19" /> 
    <circle cx="129" cy="452" r="19" /> 
    <rect x="157" y="444" rx="0" ry="0" width="89" height="11" /> 
    <rect x="11" y="486" rx="0" ry="0" width="138" height="13" /> 
    <rect x="1155" y="438" rx="0" ry="0" width="43" height="22" /> 
    <rect x="8" y="514" rx="0" ry="0" width="1200" height="5" /> 
    <circle cx="34" cy="570" r="28" /> 
    <rect x="83" y="558" rx="0" ry="0" width="123" height="10" /> 
    <rect x="83" y="576" rx="0" ry="0" width="150" height="10" /> 
    <rect x="1120" y="548" rx="0" ry="0" width="50" height="16" /> 
    <rect x="1180" y="548" rx="0" ry="0" width="19" height="16" /> 
    <rect x="8" y="613" rx="0" ry="0" width="1200" height="9" /> 
    <rect x="8" y="644" rx="5" ry="5" width="1200" height="233" /> 
    <circle cx="30" cy="917" r="19" /> 
    <circle cx="80" cy="917" r="19" /> 
    <circle cx="132" cy="917" r="19" /> 
    <rect x="160" y="909" rx="0" ry="0" width="89" height="11" /> 
    <rect x="14" y="951" rx="0" ry="0" width="138" height="13" /> 
    <rect x="1155" y="903" rx="0" ry="0" width="43" height="22" /> 
    <rect x="8" y="979" rx="0" ry="0" width="1200" height="5" />
  </ContentLoader>
)

export default BookmarkLoader;
